rows.label: tlk70000064_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh! Heroic deeds of friends
reach ears of Punpun! Truly,
friends are great adventurers!

rows.label: tlk70000064_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Friends are just like Punpun, and
that famous person who love all
people. Person called "Phil Anfropee."

rows.label: tlk70000064_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Friends say thrilling deeds of daring
"nothing much?" No! Friends should not
hide light under bushel and blush!

rows.label: tlk70000064_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Punpun hopes that friends will continue
with good-doings. Good for Punpun,
good for humanity, for Noponity!
